title: Ashton shepherd - This Is America [2013]
description:
THE NEW ASHTON SHEPHERD CD 'THIS IS AMERICA'

The new Ashton Shepherd CD 'This Is America' is officially released on Pickin' Shed Records.

The 10 song CD contains a collection of fantastic country songs by Ashton, along with a duet with the great country traditionalist, Daryle Singletary.

Ashton remains true to her country roots on this new album, giving her fans all and more of what they have come to love and expect from her.
